entry.summary:
Our paper entitled “Some ideas for non-Hermitian doping of epsilon-near-zero media” [1] received the Best Poster Award at the 13th International Congress on Engineered Material Platforms for Novel Wave Phenomena (Metamaterials), Rome, Italy, Sep. 16-19, 2019.
Coppolaro, M., Moccia, M., Castaldi, G., Engheta, N., &amp; Galdi, V. (2019). Some ideas for non-Hermitian doping of epsilon-near-zero media. In International Congress on Engineered Material Platforms for Novel Wave Phenomena (METAMATERIALS). Rome, Italy, Sep. 16-19, 2019.
